Uses of Package
com.Netzwerk.de

  • Classes in com.Netzwerk.de used by com.Netzwerk.de 
    Class and Description
    AdminServer
    This class describe a administration server which accept administrator clients
    AdminServerThread
    This class describe a thread which handle the connected administrator client
    CommandThread
    This class describe a thread of the server to control the server with commands

    Commands:
    - setmaxlimit
    - getmaxlimit
    - setxmlpath
    - getxmlpath
    - setschemapath
    - getschemapath
    - halt (to shutdown the server)
    - chadmpw
    - addadmin
    DBController
    This class describe a Database handler to get from the database and set data to the database
    DBSettings
    This class describe the database settings
    IllegalLimitException
    This exception class describe the limit exception
    IStrategy
    This interface describe the abstract methods which is to implement from the strategy algorithm classes
    Message
    This class describe a encrpyted message with salt and the parameters to decrypt it later
    Model
    This class describe a object that stores all the relevant values for the server
    - maximum Limit
    - XML file path
    - XSD file path
    - Database XML file path
    - Database XSD file path
    - Strategy algorithm
    - The advanced client option
    - The config path
    - The server port
    - The administration server port
    MyServer
    This class describe the start of the server and load the parameter.
    MyServerException
    This class describe a exceptopn if the opensockets is under 0
    SecureController
    This class describe a object which handle security things like

    - generation of hash from a password
    - generate of a salt
    - decryption and encryption of messages
    TSInfo
    This class describe a terminal server with the usage rate, the name and his type, with his IPv4 address
    XMLInterpreter
    This class describe a interpreter of the XML file.
